# Mapping
map s scroll up
map S navigate previous
map d scroll down
map D navigate next
map gt goto
map ff display_link
map rr reload
map f toggle_fullscreen
map [fullscreen] f toggle_fullscreen
map v toggle_page_mode
map w adjust_window best-fit
map W adjust_window width

# Options
set double-click-follow false
set first-page-column 1:1
set pages-per-row 2
set window-title-basename true
